race.comment: STRAPPING PROPHET (3) is knocking on the door of another win, finishing 2.2L away most recently in a CL2. This looks an easier race which he'll relish, and he did jump the equal favourite last time out. Draws the inside, maps for a lovely run and looks the one to beat. SNIPPETY LEGEND (4) resumed with a good win over this track and trip last time out when running on from the back. He rates highly on that effort and it wouldn't surprise to see him improve second-up. Can repeat the dose. BATTLE ON BATTLER (1) landed midfie3ld and got the job done over this track and trip last stat, winning by 0.5L. May need some luck from the draw, but he loves this track and trip and is racing in good order. Has to be included. MASTER ALEX (2) is better than he showed last time out and coming back in trip can see him turn in an improved performance. SWANSEE (14) is another who was disappointing last time out and can bounce back.
